    }

&lt;!-- language: lang-html --&gt;

    &lt;div id=&#39;demo&#39;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

Since you are assigning (`=`) the new value to the element, in each iteration the previous values are removed. You can either use `+=` to concatenate the new value with the previous value **OR** try with [**`insertAdjacentHTML()`**][1]: 

